EXCLUSIVE HALLOWEEN EDITION x COLLECTORS ONLY

Halloween gift to thank all the collectors who purchased my very first 2 drop on hic et nunc.

I fed an AI with my Augmented Klecksography Paintings, the so called PREMATURE artworks.
The digital metamorphosis leads to the creation of a new kind of textures and aesthetic, a PREMATURE FLESH born from what it once was acrylic augmented by digital photography.

This frame has been taken from the StyleGAN2 training at the following parameters:

Dataset: Selection of 70 PREMATURE artworks
Session Training Steps-Hours: 6000 - 6
Overall Training Steps-Hours: 9000 - 9

100 is the number I gave to the selected frame.
